  // ============================================================================
  // NOTE: Cannot disable IOG's own GeoAddons deposits for tetrahedrite,
  // chalcopyrite, vanadinite, and wulfenite via patches because AG loads
  // before IOG (alphabetically), so the interestingoregen: domain files are
  // still empty [] when AG's patches run. Instead, the variant registrations
  // in tetrahedrite-ore.json and chalcopyrite-ore.json prevent
  // "No block with code/wildcard was found" warnings. IOG's tetrahedrite,
  // vanadinite, and wulfenite entries have "enabled": false so they won't
  // generate. IOG's chalcopyrite entry (0.001 triesPerChunk) may generate
  // alongside AG's own IOG chalcopyrite deposit.
  // ============================================================================
]
